<a data-swiftype-name="resource-property" data-swiftype-type="text" href="#routetype_yaml" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">route<wbr>Type</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd><p>The type of route this is:
DEFAULT - By default, every app has routes to the local address ranges specified by RFC1918
INHERITED - Routes inherited from the real Virtual Network routes
STATIC - Static route set on the app only</p>
<p>These values will be used for syncing an app's routes with those from a Virtual Network.</p>
</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="startaddress_yaml">
<a data-swiftype-name="resource-property" data-swiftype-type="text" href="#startaddress_yaml" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">start<wbr>Address</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The starting address for this route. This may also include a CIDR notation, in which case the end address must not be specified.</dd></dl>
</pulumi-choosable>
</div>
